{
  "texts": [
    "The materialization service then frequently (for example, 1 per h) updates the associated root segments of all annotations using the ChunkedGraph (Fig. 4d, e and Extended Data Figs.",
    "3 and 5b), thereby producing a materialized version of the annotation data.",
    "Data analyses require reproducible queries to the materialized annotation data.",
    "Because ongoing proofreading and annotating make the 'live' database unsuitable for analysis queries (Fig. 5a), we create infrequent copies (for example, daily; Fig.",
    "5b) of it that serve as materialized analysis snapshots."
  ]
}